title: Paul Allen Estate refutes report that Seahawks will be sold after Super Bowl: 'The team is not for sale'

sources.name: CBS Sports NFL
sources.title: Paul Allen Estate refutes report that Seahawks will be sold after Super Bowl: 'The team is not for sale'
sources.description: The family that owns both the Seahawks and the Portland Trail Blazers refuted claims that the NFL franchise would soon be sold
